---
// Import any necessary assets if needed
---

<div class="custom-engagement-section bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Custom Engagement Model
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        For clients with unique needs, multiple systems, or evolving scopes of work—this model allows full customization.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Custom Grid Layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Top Row - Two equal cards -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <!-- Initial Consultation Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src="src/assets/pricing/icon_1.png" alt="Consultation Icon" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500"/>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                Initial Consultation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We begin with a discovery meeting to understand your company's structure, accounting pain points, operational complexity, and financial goals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <!-- Seamless Software Integration Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-start" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src="src/assets/pricing/icon_2.png" alt="Integration Icon" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500"/>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                Seamless Software Integration
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Whether you're using legacy systems or modern platforms, we assist with full financial data migration, cleanup, and configuration to ensure operational continuity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Meet Your Dedicated Team Card - Right side, spans 2 rows -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1 lg:row-span-2">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="flex flex-col h-full">

            <div class="flex items-start" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
              <!-- Icon -->
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="src/assets/pricing/icon_3.png" alt="Integration Icon" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500"/>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <!-- Icon -->
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                  Meet Your Dedicated Team
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                  You'll be introduced to a specialized FinKeepers accounting pod—led by a dedicated manager—who will coordinate ongoing service delivery and be your primary point of contact.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium mb-2">This model is ideal for:</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-6">
                <li>• Venture-backed startups or SMBs with evolving needs</li>
                <li>• Businesses undergoing restructuring or audit prep</li>
                <li>• Clients requiring integrations across multiple tools/platforms</li>
                <li>• Complex chart of accounts or industry-specific compliance</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Call Button - positioned at bottom -->
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <button class="w-full bg-white border-2 border-orange-500 text-orange-500 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                Call
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom Row - Tailored Proposal spans 2 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <!-- Tailored Proposal & Onboarding Card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          
          <div class="flex items-start" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
              <!-- Icon -->
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <img src="src/assets/pricing/icon_4.png" alt="Integration Icon" class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500"/>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <!-- Icon -->
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                  Tailored Proposal & Onboarding
                </h3>
                <div class="lg:flex lg:gap-8">
                <div class="lg:flex-1">
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Following the consultation, we prepare a personalized proposal detailing:
                  </p>
                  <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-4">
                    <li>• Recommended services</li>
                    <li>• Expected timelines</li>
                    <li>• Custom pricing based on complexity and volume</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Once approved, we finalize the engagement agreement and begin onboarding.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .custom-engagement-section {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
  }

  /* Custom hover shadow */
  .hover\:shadow-lg:hover {
    box-shadow: 0px 1px 11.1px 1px #ED7C0029;
  }

  /* Custom grid layout */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .lg\:col-span-1,
    .lg\:col-span-2,
    .lg\:row-span-2 {
      grid-column: span 1 !important;
      grid-row: span 1 !important;
    }
  }
</style>